Here is an SQL query, using a JOIN, to find Rockbuster inventory by film category.

SELECT C.category_id,
C.name,
COUNT (inventory_id) AS inventory_of_film
FROM inventory A
LEFT JOIN film_category B ON A.film_id = B.film_id
LEFT JOIN category C ON B.category_id = C.category_id
GROUP BY C.category_id,
C.name
ORDER BY inventory_of_film DESC

